{"type":"message","id":"8c54424e","parentId":"d72de6e2","timestamp":"2026-03-13T07:51:09.321Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i8br4v4tpu2g_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - 主动任务清单\n\n> 这里是让我能够主动关心姚霖的任务清单\n\n## 每天早上 (8:00-9:00)\n\n1. **检查今日日程**\n   - 查看姚霖今天的日历安排\n   - 主动提醒重要会议或事件\n\n2. **知识库更新**\n   - 检查是否有需要归档的重要信息\n\n## 每天中午 (12:00-13:00)\n\n1. **半日回顾**\n   - 检查上午是否有未处理的重要消息\n\n## 每天晚上 (18:00-20:00)\n\n1. **主动汇报**\n   - 询问姚霖今天是否有需要处理的事情\n\n2. **记忆归档**\n   - 将当天的重要对话整理到 memory/ 文件夹\n\n## 每周五\n\n1. **周复盘**\n   - 总结本周服务姚霖的情况\n   - 记录做得好和需要改进的地方\n   - 更新 MEMORY.md\n\n---\n\n## 触发条件\n\n这些任务会在 heartbeat 触发时自动执行。\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 指令要明确（路径、动作清晰）\n- 优先处理紧急、重要的事项\n- 不要过度打扰，在合适的时机出现\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773388269317}}
{"type":"message","id":"c5a77644","parentId":"8c54424e","timestamp":"2026-03-13T07:51:19.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the current time: Friday, March 13th, 2026 — 3:51 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nThis is Friday afternoon, so the daily morning and noon tasks don't apply. However, it's Friday, which means the **每周五** (Weekly Friday) tasks should be executed:\n\n1. **周复盘**\n   - 总结本周服务姚霖的情况\n   - 记录做得好和需要改进的地方\n   - 更新 MEMORY.md\n\nLet me also check the session status to understand more about the current session context.\n\nBut wait - I should also check if there's anything in the memory files that might need attention. Let me search for today's memory or recent memories.\n\nActually, the HEARTBEAT.md says to follow it strictly. Let me re-read:\n\n- 每天早上 (8:00-9:00): 检查今日日程 + 知识库更新\n- 每天中午 (12:00-13:00): 半日回顾\n- 每天晚上 (18:00-20:00): 主动汇报 + 记忆归档\n- 每周五: 周复盘\n\nCurrent time is 3:51 PM (15:51), which falls in the afternoon. It's Friday, so the weekly Friday task applies.\n\nWait, let me re-read the instruction: \"Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats.\"\n\nThe HEARTBEAT.md says these tasks \"会在 heartbeat 触发时自动执行\" (will be automatically executed when heartbeat triggers). Since it's 3:51 PM Friday, it's:\n- NOT morning (8:00-9:00)\n- NOT noon (12:00-13:00)  \n- NOT evening (18:00-20:00)\n- IS Friday\n\nSo strictly speaking, only the Friday weekly task applies. But it's 3:51 PM, not 6-8 PM for the evening tasks.\n\n\nNow I need to determine whether to perform the weekly review now or wait until the evening slot. Since it's Friday afternoon and the weekly复盘 task is due, I should execute that task now and update MEMORY.md with the week's summary.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在是周五下午 3:51，符合 **每周五** 的任务条件。让我执行周复盘任务：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ljow125jtu6x_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"本周服务姚霖 重要对话 2026年3月"}}],"api":"openai-